<div class="w3-row-padding"><h3>서비스 선택</h3></div>
<div class="w3-container w3-border w3-padding-16">
    <div class="w3-row">
        <div class="w3-col m5">
            <div class="w3-row">
                <div class="w3-col s12">
                    <div class="w3-container">
                        <img src="http://www.oho.co.kr/images/v_img/pop_box01.png" class="w3-border">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w3-col m7 w3-padding-8">
            <b>방학내내 안심하고 맡기는 대학생 전용 서비스</b>
            <div class="w3-panel w3-small">
                대학교의 방학기간동안 한시적으로 운영하는 서비스입니다.<br/>
                학교별 일시는 오호캠퍼스 에서 확인바랍니다.<br/>
                오호 캠퍼스 전용박스 비용과 보관비, 운송비 포함<br/>
                행사 당일에 박스를 전달해 드리고 포장 후 맡겨주시면 됩니다.
            </div>

            <div class="w3-panel w3-right-align"><b>방학내내 <br/> 1박스: 12,000원</b></div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="w3-container w3-padding-8 w3-border-top">
        <div class="w3-row">
            <div class="w3-col m3 s12"><h4>수량/기간</h4></div>
            <div class="w3-col m9 s12">

                <div class="w3-row w3-padding-4">
                    <div class="w3-col m3 s3">전용박스</div>
                    <div class="w3-col m3 s3"><input class="w3-input w3-border" type="text" can-value="stocks.0.qty" /></div>
                    <div class="w3-col m6 s6"> <span class="w3-margin-left">개 (오호 전용박스)</span></div>
                </div>


                {{#hasError stocks.0}}
                    <div class="w3-row"><span class="w3-red">{{stocks.0.error.qty.0}}</span></div>
                {{/hasError}}

                <div class="w3-row w3-padding-4">
                    <div class="w3-col m3 s3">개인박스</div>
                    <div class="w3-col m3 s3"><input class="w3-input w3-border" type="text" can-value="stocks.1.qty"/></div>
                    <div class="w3-col m6 s6"> <span class="w3-margin-left">개 (다른 박스사용)</span></div>
                </div>

                {{#hasError stocks.1}}
                    <div class="w3-row"><span class="w3-red">{{stocks.1.error.qty.0}}</span></div>
                {{/hasError}}

                <div class="w3-row w3-padding-4">
                    <div class="w3-col m3 s3">비규격</div>
                    <div class="w3-col m3 s3"><input class="w3-input w3-border" type="text" can-value="stocks.2.qty" /></div>
                    <div class="w3-col m6 s6"> <span class="w3-margin-left">개</span></div>
                </div>

                {{#hasError stocks.2}}
                    <div class="w3-row"><span class="w3-red">{{stocks.2.error.qty.0}}</span></div>
                {{/hasError}}

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="w3-container w3-padding-8  w3-border-top">
        <div class="w3-row">
            <div class="w3-col m3 s12"><h4>학교선택</h4></div>
            <div class="w3-col m9 s12">
                <div class="w3-container">
                    <select  class="w3-select w3-white">
                        <option>학교를 선택하세요</option>
                        {{#schools}}
                            <option value="{{id}}">{{name}}</option>
                        {{/schools}}
                    </select>
                </div>

                {{#school}}
                <div class="w3-container w3-padding-16">
                    <div class="w3-row">
                        <div class="w3-col m4">
                            <img src="{{school.logo}}" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="w3-col m4">
                            <b>{{school.name}}</b>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/school}}
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>


    <div class="w3-container w3-padding-8  w3-border-top">
        <div class="w3-row">
            <div class="w3-col m3 s12"><h4>결제금액</h4></div>
            <div class="w3-col m9 s12 w3-right-align">
                {{#stocks}}
                {{#if qty}}
                <div class="w3-row w3-padding-4">
                    <div class="w3-col m3 s3">{{name}}</div>
                    <div class="w3-col m4 s4">{{qty}}개</div>
                    <div class="w3-col m5 s5">{{subTotal}} 원</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{/stocks}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {{stocks.total}}
</div>


<div class="w3-row-padding"><h3>주문자 정보</h3></div>
<div class="w3-container w3-border w3-padding-16">
    <div class="w3-row w3-padding-4">
        <div class="w3-col m3 s12">주문자명</div>
        <div class="w3-col m5 s12">
            <input class="w3-input w3-border" type="text" can-value="customer.name" />
            {{#hasError customer 'name'}}
                <span class="w3-red">{{customer.error.name.0}}</span>
            {{/hasError}}

        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="w3-row w3-padding-4">
        <div class="w3-col m3 s12">핸드폰</div>
        <div class="w3-col m5 s12">
            <input class="w3-input w3-border" type="text" can-value="customer.tel" />
            {{#hasError customer 'tel'}}
                <span class="w3-red">{{customer.error.tel.0}}</span>
            {{/hasError}}
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-row w3-padding-4">
        <div class="w3-col m3 s12">이메일</div>
        <div class="w3-col m5 s12">
            <input class="w3-input w3-border" type="text" can-value="customer.email"/>
            {{#hasError customer 'email'}}
                <span class="w3-red">{{customer.error.email.0}}</span>
            {{/hasError}}
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-row w3-padding-4">
        <div class="w3-col m3 s12">메모</div>
        <div class="w3-col m5 s12">
            <textarea class="w3-input w3-border" data-attr="memo" can-value="customer.memo"></textarea>
            <div class="w3-panel w3-small">
                1층 출입문이 잠겨 있는 경우 비밀번호를 남겨 주시면 더 수월하게 배송이 가능합니다 <br/>
                회수하는 곳의 주소가 다를 경우에도 메모를 남겨주세요
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="w3-row-padding">
    <div class="w3-panel w3-right-align">
        <button class="w3-btn w3-border w3-white w3-large" id="cart">장바구니 담기</button>
        <button class="w3-btn w3-border w3-white w3-large" id="next2">다음 단계</button>
    </div>
</div>
